text: Kate Hinrichs (born 16 February 2000) is a South African water polo player. She competed for the South Africa women's national water polo team in the 2019 World Aquatics Championships. She played for Long Island University's women's waterpolo team. == References == == Other websites == * kate-hinrichs * Class of 2019 Signings LIU Category:2002 births Category:Living people Category:South African water polo players
